com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport
Class CommandList

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport.CommandList

public final class CommandList
extends Object

A sequence of ICommands from a particular client session that should be executed in order, according to the CommandListOptions in force.

Validation:

  • A CommandList must not contain a TakeLeaseOnLatestItem command that involves a particular Item before an AmendCardOnItem or a DeleteCardFromItem command involving the same Item. For these commands, you must take the lease with TakeLeaseOnSpecificItem.

Since:
1.0
